headline: The New Sandisk Coming Soon
summary: MILPITAS, Calif., December 17, 2024--Sandisk Corporation today previewed its new corporate branding and creative direction, signaling a bold debut of the company’s comeback launch as a standalone Flash and memory technology innovator, planned for early 2025.
